/#
   A type defining a term of the formula. Its value is the product of the its coefficient and the referenced partial derivatives.
 #/
record FpML5.confirmation.FormulaTerm {
  # The coefficient by which this term is multiplied, typically 1 or -1.
  coefficient : decimal

  # A reference to the partial derivative.
  partialDerivativeReference : FpML5.confirmation.PricingParameterDerivativeReference

}

coefficient.Doc: The coefficient by which this term is multiplied, typically 1 or -1.
coefficient.Name: coefficient

partialDerivativeReference.Doc: A reference to the partial derivative.
partialDerivativeReference.Name: partialDerivativeReference
